				<wikidot:authorName>Derpp Potat</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4052566</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>On 04/08/2005, it was noted during a routine entry into SCP-3081 that SCP-3081-1R-5 had formed itself into an OK gesture, while SCP-3081-1L-2 repeatedly inserted and removed its thumb from the &quot;O&quot;. This action continued for the full length of time personnel were present in SCP-3081. (1 hour, 25 minutes.)</p> </blockquote> <p>Yes. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
