					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-3513467#post-3582390</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-3513467/scp-3081#post-3582390</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 31 Aug 2017 14:40:02 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Person Man Guy</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2332930</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>For a simple concept, this was really well executed.</p> <p>You knew the Containment Procedures wouldn't be very interesting, so you got them over quick. Within the first footnote, I was hooked; you see &quot;extradimensional space&quot; a lot on this site, and I'm glad you used that footnote, because unlike other uses of that phrase, I actually did a double take at the dimensions.</p> <p>I started cringing from the second paragraph. This is a compliment, by the way; you were really good at making this concept as weird and surreal as possible. Smaller things like the little moan by the malformed baby hand, the word &quot;slurry&quot; to describe visera, and the weird font choices in the letter really exemplified the creepy feel of this.</p> <p>Easy +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
