					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-3513467#post-3582333</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-3513467/scp-3081#post-3582333</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 31 Aug 2017 13:20:05 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>TL333s</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1304786</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p><tt>W E A T S O F T H A N D S ® A P P R O V E T H I S M E S S A G E</tt></p> <p>Like I told people in chat, when in doubt, just do what worked last time. &lt;.&lt;</p> <p>I was just driving through rural Ohio recently and got this mental image of giant hands acting like cows. One thing led to another, and I said, <em>what if they were making hand milk</em>, and this popped out. The meaning of what &quot;hand milk&quot; is has changed a bit from the original concept. (RIP, Delicious Milk Consistency Act takedowns.)</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kid-f" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2782678&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1504186001" alt="Kid F" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2782678)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kid-f" >Kid F</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2156983&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1504186001" alt="psul" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2156983)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" >psul</a></span> for feedback.</p> <p>Image by <a href="https://jenninexus.smugmug.com/IOS-folder/Nature/i-Pg9d9Pw/A">jenninexus</a>, licensed under CC.</p> <p><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">I swear to god if Soft Hands becomes my first GoI I am going to shoot myself</span></p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
